data.name: TextBox1.Text
data.value: "Hey baby, come and get me!" Handsome Bella was found roaming around a compound looking for love. Despite attempts to find his family he had other ideas, and has been camped out in forest care awaiting his journey to the UK to find his one true love. He has written his own profile(via his foster mummy). I'm a handsome fluffy male with the mane of lion and the hart of a teddy bear. I spend a lot of time outdoors, just looking at the birds and lying in the sun. I'm very cuddly, both with adults and with children, although when the kids make too much moise i prefer a quiet spot. I'm quite talkative, when its time for food but also when in check to see who's home and be chased...the rest of the time I relax in and around the house, washing, sleeping, eating... So if you're looking for a fit and healthy, easy loving companion that's good with kids( and is good looking too!) I might just be your guy!
